specialize hunif (a + (↑j + 1) * (b - a) / ↑n) hx1
  specialize hunif (a + (↑ℓ + ↑j * ↑k + 1) * (b - a) / (↑n * ↑k)) hx2
```

The difference in function values is less than `ε`:

