```

This is using the property `|A * B| ≤ |A| * |B|`. The sum is positive, so we can remove the absolute value.

Now, we can bound the sum:

```tactics
have h6 : ∑ j ∈ range n, ∑ ℓ ∈ range k, |f (a + (↑ℓ + ↑j * ↑k + 1) * (b - a) / (↑n * ↑k)) - f (a + (↑j + 1) * (b - a) / ↑n)| ≤ n * k * ε := by
